{"_id": "bg001", "name": "Background: Adeptus Administratum", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Commerce or Medicae, Common Lore (Adeptus Administratum), Linguistics (High Gothic), Logic, Scholastic Lore (any)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Las or SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Laspistol or stub auto, Imperial robes, autoquill, Chrono, dataslate, medi-kit\n\nBackground Bonus: Master of Paperwork: count Availability of all items as one level more available.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Knowledge or Social", "benefit": "Aptitude: Knowledge or Social | Master of Paperwork: count Availability of all items as one level more available."}}
{"_id": "bg002", "name": "Background: Adeptus Arbites", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Awareness, Common Lore (Adeptus Arbites, Underworld), Inquiry or Interrogation, Intimidate, Scrutiny\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Shock or SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Shotgun or shock maul, Enforcer carapace, 3 doses stimm, manacles, 12 lho sticks\n\nBackground Bonus: The Face of the Law: substitute WP bonus for DoS on Intimidation and Interrogation tests.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Offence or Defence", "benefit": "Aptitude: Offence or Defence | The Face of the Law: substitute WP bonus for DoS on Intimidation and Interrogation tests."}}
{"_id": "bg003", "name": "Background: Adeptus Astra Telepathica", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Awareness, Common Lore (Adeptus Astra Telepathica), Deceive or Interrogation, Forbidden Lore (the Warp), Psyniscience or Scrutiny\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Las, Low-Tech)\n\nStarting Equipment: Laspistol, staff or whip, light flak cloak, micro-bead or psy focus\n\nBackground Bonus: The Constant Threat: increase or decrease Psychic Phenomena result by WP bonus.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Defence or Psyker", "benefit": "Aptitude: Defence or Psyker | The Constant Threat: increase or decrease Psychic Phenomena result by WP bonus."}}
{"_id": "bg004", "name": "Background: Adeptus Mechanicus", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Awareness or Operate (any), Common Lore (Adeptus Mechanicus), Logic, Security, Tech-Use\n\nStarting Talents: Mechadendrite Use (Utility), Weapon Training (SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Autogun or hand cannon, optical Mechadendrite, Imperial robes, 2 vials sacred unguents\n\nBackground Bonus: Replace the Weak Flesh: count Availability of all cybernetics as two levels more available. Starts with Mechanicus Implants.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Knowledge or Tech", "benefit": "Aptitude: Knowledge or Tech | Replace the Weak Flesh: count Availability of all cybernetics as two levels more available. Starts with Mechanicus Implants."}}
{"_id": "bg005", "name": "Background: Adeptus Ministorum", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Charm, Command, Common Lore (Adeptus Ministorum), Inquiry or Scrutiny, Linguistics (High Gothic)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Flame) or Weapon Training (Low-Tech, SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Hand flamer or Warhammer + stub revolver, Imperial robes or flak vest, glow-globe\n\nBackground Bonus: Faith is All: when spending Fate point for +10 bonus, gain +20 instead.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Leadership or Social", "benefit": "Aptitude: Leadership or Social | Faith is All: when spending Fate point for +10 bonus, gain +20 instead."}}
{"_id": "bg006", "name": "Background: Imperial Guard", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Athletics, Command, Common Lore (Imperial Guard), Medicae or Operate (Surface), Navigate (Surface)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Las, Low-Tech)\n\nStarting Equipment: Lasgun or laspistol + sword, combat vest, flak armour, grapnel, 12 lho sticks, magnoculars\n\nBackground Bonus: Hammer of the Emperor: when attacking a target an ally attacked since your last turn, re-roll damage results of 1 or 2.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Leadership", "benefit": "Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Leadership | Hammer of the Emperor: when attacking a target an ally attacked since your last turn, re-roll damage results of 1 or 2."}}
{"_id": "bg007", "name": "Background: Outcast", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Acrobatics or Sleight of Hand, Common Lore (Underworld), Deceive, Dodge, Stealth\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Chain, Las or SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Autopistol or laspistol, chainsword, armoured body glove, injector, 2 doses obscura\n\nBackground Bonus: Never Quit: count Toughness bonus as two higher for purposes of determining Fatigue.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Social", "benefit": "Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Social | Never Quit: count Toughness bonus as two higher for purposes of determining Fatigue."}}
{"_id": "bg008", "name": "Background: Adepta Sororitas", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Athletics, Charm or Intimidate, Common Lore (Adepta Sororitas), Linguistics (High Gothic), Medicae or Parry\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Flame or Las, Chain)\n\nStarting Equipment: Hand flamer or laspistol, chainblade, armoured bodyglove, chrono, micro-bead\n\nBackground Bonus: Incorruptible Devotion: when gaining Corruption Points, gain that many Insanity Points minus 1 (minimum 0) instead.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Offence or Social", "benefit": "Aptitude: Offence or Social | Incorruptible Devotion: when gaining Corruption Points, gain that many Insanity Points minus 1 (minimum 0) instead."}}
{"_id": "bg009", "name": "Background: Mutant", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Acrobatics or Athletics, Awareness, Deceive or Intimidate, Forbidden Lore (Mutants), Survival\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Low-Tech, SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Shotgun or stub revolver + great weapon, grapnel, heavy leathers, 2 doses stimm\n\nBackground Bonus: Twisted Flesh: always choose to fail tests resisting malignancy/mutation. Gains one starting Trait. Starts with 10 Corruption.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Offence", "benefit": "Aptitude: Fieldcraft or Offence | Twisted Flesh: always choose to fail tests resisting malignancy/mutation. Gains one starting Trait. Starts with 10 Corruption."}}
{"_id": "bg010", "name": "Background: Heretek", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Deceive or Inquiry, Forbidden Lore (any), Medicae or Security, Tech-Use, Trade (any)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Stub revolver, 1 web grenade, combi-tool, flak cloak, filtration plugs, de-tox, dataslate\n\nBackground Bonus: Master of Hidden Lores: +20 Tech-Use for unfamiliar devices if you have relevant Forbidden Lore. Starts with Mechanicus Implants.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Finesse or Tech", "benefit": "Aptitude: Finesse or Tech | Master of Hidden Lores: +20 Tech-Use for unfamiliar devices if you have relevant Forbidden Lore. Starts with Mechanicus Implants."}}
{"_id": "bg011", "name": "Background: Imperial Navy", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Athletics, Command or Intimidate, Common Lore (Imperial Navy), Navigate (Stellar), Operate (Aeronautica or Voidship)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Chain or Shock, SP)\n\nStarting Equipment: Combat shotgun or hand cannon, chainsword or shock whip, flak coat, rebreather, micro-bead\n\nBackground Bonus: Close Quarters Discipline: score one additional DoS on successful BS tests against targets at Point-Blank, Short range, or in melee.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Offence or Tech", "benefit": "Aptitude: Offence or Tech | Close Quarters Discipline: score one additional DoS on successful BS tests against targets at Point-Blank, Short range, or in melee."}}
{"_id": "bg012", "name": "Background: Rogue Trader Fleet", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Charm or Scrutiny, Commerce, Common Lore (Rogue Traders), Linguistics (any alien), Operate (Surface or Aeronautica)\n\nStarting Talents: Weapon Training (Las or SP, Shock)\n\nStarting Equipment: Laspistol or autopistol (Compact), shock maul, mesh cloak or carapace chestplate, auspex, chrono\n\nBackground Bonus: Inured to the Xenos: +10 Fear tests caused by aliens, +20 Interaction tests with alien characters.\n\nBackground Aptitude: Finesse or Social", "benefit": "Aptitude: Finesse or Social | Inured to the Xenos: +10 Fear tests caused by aliens, +20 Interaction tests with alien characters."}}
{"_id": "ro001", "name": "Role: Assassin", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Agility, BS or WS, Fieldcraft, Finesse, Perception\n\nRole Talent: Jaded or Leap Up\n\nRole Bonus: Sure Kill: spend Fate after successful hit to add DoS on attack roll as bonus damage.", "benefit": "Sure Kill: spend Fate after successful hit to add DoS on attack roll as bonus damage."}}
{"_id": "ro002", "name": "Role: Chirurgeon", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Fieldcraft, Intelligence, Knowledge, Strength, Toughness\n\nRole Talent: Resistance (any) or Takedown\n\nRole Bonus: Dedicated Healer: spend Fate to automatically succeed on a failed First Aid test with DoS equal to Int bonus.", "benefit": "Dedicated Healer: spend Fate to automatically succeed on a failed First Aid test with DoS equal to Int bonus."}}
{"_id": "ro003", "name": "Role: Desperado", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Agility, BS, Defence, Fellowship, Finesse\n\nRole Talent: Catfall or Quick Draw\n\nRole Bonus: Move and Shoot: once per round after a Move action, make a single Standard Attack with a Pistol as Free Action.", "benefit": "Move and Shoot: once per round after a Move action, make a single Standard Attack with a Pistol as Free Action."}}
{"_id": "ro004", "name": "Role: Hierophant", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Fellowship, Offence, Social, Toughness, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Double Team or Hatred (any)\n\nRole Bonus: Sway the Masses: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Charm, Command, or Intimidate with DoS equal to WP bonus.", "benefit": "Sway the Masses: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Charm, Command, or Intimidate with DoS equal to WP bonus."}}
{"_id": "ro005", "name": "Role: Mystic", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Defence, Intelligence, Knowledge, Perception, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Resistance (Psychic Powers) or Warp Sense\n\nRole Bonus: Stare into the Warp: starts with the Psyker elite advance.", "benefit": "Stare into the Warp: starts with the Psyker elite advance."}}
{"_id": "ro006", "name": "Role: Sage", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Intelligence, Knowledge, Perception, Tech, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Ambidextrous or Clues from the Crowds\n\nRole Bonus: Quest for Knowledge: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Logic or any Lore test with DoS equal to Int bonus.", "benefit": "Quest for Knowledge: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Logic or any Lore test with DoS equal to Int bonus."}}
{"_id": "ro007", "name": "Role: Seeker", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Fellowship, Intelligence, Perception, Social, Tech\n\nRole Talent: Keen Intuition or Disarm\n\nRole Bonus: Nothing Escapes My Sight: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Awareness or Inquiry with DoS equal to Per bonus.", "benefit": "Nothing Escapes My Sight: spend Fate to automatically succeed at Awareness or Inquiry with DoS equal to Per bonus."}}
{"_id": "ro008", "name": "Role: Warrior", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: BS, Defence, Offence, Strength, Weapon Skill\n\nRole Talent: Iron Jaw or Rapid Reload\n\nRole Bonus: Expert at Violence: spend Fate after successful attack to substitute WS or BS bonus for the DoS on the attack.", "benefit": "Expert at Violence: spend Fate after successful attack to substitute WS or BS bonus for the DoS on the attack."}}
{"_id": "ro009", "name": "Role: Crusader", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Knowledge, Offence, Strength, Toughness, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Bodyguard or Deny the Witch\n\nRole Bonus: Smite the Unholy: spend Fate to automatically pass a Fear test. Melee hits vs Fear (X) creatures deal X extra damage and X higher Penetration.", "benefit": "Smite the Unholy: spend Fate to automatically pass a Fear test. Melee hits vs Fear (X) creatures deal X extra damage and X higher Penetration."}}
{"_id": "hw001", "name": "Homeworld: Feral World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Str +X, Tou +X | Fel -X | Fate 2 | Blessing 3+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: The Old Ways: Low-Tech weapons lose Primitive, gain Proven (3). Aptitude: Toughness | Wounds: 9+1d5", "benefit": "The Old Ways: Low-Tech weapons lose Primitive, gain Proven (3). Aptitude: Toughness | Wounds: 9+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw002", "name": "Homeworld: Forge World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Int +X, Tou +X | Fel -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 8+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Omnissiah's Chosen: gain Technical Knock or Weapon-Tech. Aptitude: Intelligence | Wounds: 8+1d5", "benefit": "Omnissiah's Chosen: gain Technical Knock or Weapon-Tech. Aptitude: Intelligence | Wounds: 8+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw003", "name": "Homeworld: Highborn", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Fel +X, Influence +X | Tou -X | Fate 4 | Blessing 10+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Breeding Counts: reduce Influence losses by 1 (minimum 1). Aptitude: Fellowship | Wounds: 9+1d5", "benefit": "Breeding Counts: reduce Influence losses by 1 (minimum 1). Aptitude: Fellowship | Wounds: 9+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw004", "name": "Homeworld: Hive World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Ag +X, Per +X | WP -X | Fate 2 | Blessing 6+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Teeming Masses: move through crowds as open terrain. +20 Navigate (Surface) in closed spaces. Aptitude: Perception | Wounds: 8+1d5", "benefit": "Teeming Masses: move through crowds as open terrain. +20 Navigate (Surface) in closed spaces. Aptitude: Perception | Wounds: 8+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw005", "name": "Homeworld: Shrine World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Fel +X, WP +X | Per -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 6+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Faith in the Creed: when spending Fate, not reduced on 1d10 roll of 1. Aptitude: Willpower | Wounds: 8+1d5", "benefit": "Faith in the Creed: when spending Fate, not reduced on 1d10 roll of 1. Aptitude: Willpower | Wounds: 8+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw006", "name": "Homeworld: Voidborn", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Int +X, WP +X | Str -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 5+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Child of the Dark: start with Strong Minded. +30 tests in zero-gravity. Aptitude: Intelligence | Wounds: 7+1d5", "benefit": "Child of the Dark: start with Strong Minded. +30 tests in zero-gravity. Aptitude: Intelligence | Wounds: 7+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw007", "name": "Homeworld: Agri-World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Fel +X, Str +X | Ag -X | Fate 2 | Blessing 7+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Strength from the Land: start with Brutal Charge (2) Trait. Aptitude: Strength | Wounds: 8+1d5", "benefit": "Strength from the Land: start with Brutal Charge (2) Trait. Aptitude: Strength | Wounds: 8+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw008", "name": "Homeworld: Feudal World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Per +X, WS +X | Int -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 6+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: At Home in Armour: ignore maximum Agility value imposed by any worn armour. Aptitude: Weapon Skill | Wounds: 9+1d5", "benefit": "At Home in Armour: ignore maximum Agility value imposed by any worn armour. Aptitude: Weapon Skill | Wounds: 9+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw009", "name": "Homeworld: Frontier World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: BS +X, Per +X | Fel -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 7+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Rely on None but Yourself: +20 Tech-Use for weapon modifications, +10 repairing items. Aptitude: Ballistic Skill | Wounds: 7+1d5", "benefit": "Rely on None but Yourself: +20 Tech-Use for weapon modifications, +10 repairing items. Aptitude: Ballistic Skill | Wounds: 7+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw010", "name": "Homeworld: Death World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Ag +X, Per +X | Fel -X | Fate 2 | Blessing 5+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Survivor's Paranoia: while Surprised, attackers do not gain normal +30 bonus. Aptitude: Fieldcraft | Wounds: 9+1d5", "benefit": "Survivor's Paranoia: while Surprised, attackers do not gain normal +30 bonus. Aptitude: Fieldcraft | Wounds: 9+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw011", "name": "Homeworld: Garden World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: Fel +X, Ag +X | Tou -X | Fate 2 | Blessing 4+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Serenity of the Green: halve duration of Shock/Mental Trauma. Remove Insanity for 50xp not 100xp. Aptitude: Social | Wounds: 7+1d5", "benefit": "Serenity of the Green: halve duration of Shock/Mental Trauma. Remove Insanity for 50xp not 100xp. Aptitude: Social | Wounds: 7+1d5"}}
{"_id": "hw012", "name": "Homeworld: Daemon World", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Characteristics: WP +X, Per +X | Fel -X | Fate 3 | Blessing 4+\n\nHomeworld Bonus: Touched by the Warp: start with Rank 1 Psyniscience. Begin with 1d10+5 Corruption. Aptitude: Willpower | Wounds: 7+1d5", "benefit": "Touched by the Warp: start with Rank 1 Psyniscience. Begin with 1d10+5 Corruption. Aptitude: Willpower | Wounds: 7+1d5"}}
